ComponentAtomicModelDescriptor - Class in fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.plugins.devs.architectures
The class ComponentAtomicModelDescriptor implements a descriptor of a DEVS atomic model that is held by a BCM component in a BCM component assembly; using the DEVS closure over composition property, the model actually created by the BCM component can be a coupled model but it will be described as an atomic one in the global architecture for the interconnection.

ComponentCoupledModelDescriptor - Class in fr.sorbonne_u.components.cyphy.plugins.devs.architectures
The class ComponentCoupledModelDescriptorimplements a descriptor of a DEVS coupled models that is held by a BCM component in a BCM component assembly, associating their URI, their static information including the mapping to the holding component in the assembly, as well as an optional factory that can be used to instantiate a coupled model object to run simulations.
